==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Freshness
<hw>Fresh"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being
fresh.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Scots had the advantage both for number and
<qex>freshness</qex>⟦br⟧
of men.</q> <rj><qau>Hayward.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And breathe the <qex>freshness</qex> of the open air.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Her cheeks their <qex>freshness</qex> lose and wonted grace.</q>
<rj><qau>Granville.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fresh-new</ent>⟦br⟧
